Tilt Brush is a room-scale 3D painting virtual reality application available from Google, originally developed by Skillman & Hackett.
Introducing Tilt Brush. Paint life-size three-dimensional brush strokes, stars, light, and even fire. Experience painting as you have never before

To paint in 3D with Tilt Brush, you'll need to have an HTC Vive, an Oculus Rift, or a Windows Mixed Reality headset with Touch controllers
